Peter Curtin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Peter_Curtin 0 Peter Julian Curtin (31 January 1944 – 18 May 2014) was an Australian television and stage actor, whose career began when he joined the Melbourne Theatre Company, appearing in The Plough and the Stars with Wendy Hughes.
